'''Bolivia''' (bhâsa Spanyol: ''Bolivia; Estado Plurinacional de Bolivia'') panèka sala sèttong naghârâ è [[Amerika Lao']]. Embu' koṭṭana iyâ arèya [[Sucre]] bân [[La Paz]], bân koṭṭa palèng rajâ iyâ arèya [[Santa Cruz de la Sierra]]. Loas bilajâhna iyâ arèya 1,098,581 km². Pendudukna iyâ arèya 11,428,245 (2019) bân kapadatan pendudukna 10 orèng per km².<ref>[https://www.imf.org/en/Publications/SPROLLs/world-economic-outlook-databases#sort=%40imfdate%20descending "Report for Selected Countries and Subjects". International Monetary Fund.]</ref>

